<paragraph base="F7282575" principles="yes" id="IFRS01_7"><paranum>7</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 1"/><data name="paranum" value="7"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS01_P0050">An entity shall use the same accounting policies in its <xref base="F7282735" href="IFRS01_APPA.dita#IFRS01_APPA/IFRS01_P0237">opening IFRS statement of financial position<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0267"/></ph></xref> and throughout all periods presented in its<xref base="F7282731" href="IFRS01_APPA.dita#IFRS01_APPA/IFRS01_P0227"> first IFRS financial statements<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0133"/></ph></xref>. Those accounting policies shall comply with each IFRS effective at the end of its <i>first IFRS reporting period</i>, except as specified in <xref base="F9049116" href="IFRS01_g13-17.dita#IFRS01_g13-17/IFRS01_g13-17_TI" id="IFRS01_X0114">paragraphs 13&#x2013;19</xref> and <xref base="F8305642" href="IFRS01_APPB.dita" scope="local" id="IFRS01_X0115">Appendices B&#x2013;E</xref>.</p></body></paragraph>